## Trip buddies sheet (`trip_members_bottom_sheet.dart`)
- Utility sheet (pattern B): `SheetScaffold` + `SheetSectionHeader` + `SheetSoftCard`
- Headline count: `SpendGlassShell` (liquid glass) — not solid teal blocks
- Rows: `BuddyAvatar` + name + optional email subtitle
- Role control: `SheetChoiceChipRow` (**View** / **Edit**) — not `SegmentedButton`
- Entry: trip summary people row (chevron) or Share → **Trip buddies & access**

## Tools tab (`2_tools/`)
- Nav label **Tools**; page title **Tools** (title-only AppBar).
- Sections: Travel kits → Essentials → Japan → More.
- Working tools open utility sheets following pattern B above.
- **Live** tools: Currency, Units, Time zones, Mapcode (`ToolsPage.isLive`).
- **Coming soon** tiles: `opacity 0.38`, `Pressable(onTap: null)`, **Soon** badge — no snackbar.
- Converter amounts: `SheetNumericHeroField` (large tabular figures + affix).

## Liquid glass summary cards
- Trip **Spend** / **Plan** today & total snapshots use frosted glass — see `liquid-glass-ui.mdc`.
- Do **not** regress to solid `primaryDark` hero blocks for inline metrics.

## Tab shells & empty states
- Tab-root pages use transparent scaffold + `extendBody` — see `app-shell-ui.mdc`.
- Global Spend wallet patterns (`SpendWalletCard`, `SpendListCard`) — see `app-shell-ui.mdc` + `liquid-glass-ui.mdc`.
- Cards & section titles (`TripCard`, `SectionHeader`, …) — see `ui-cards-and-sections.mdc`.
- Profile / Me settings — see `profile-me-ui.mdc`.
